cdl_table_config		
		
Column Name	Data Type	Description
table_id	STRING	Unique logical ID (e.g., acc_t1_to_fac_t1) [1].
source_system	STRING	Source system name (e.g., ACCOUNT_DB) [1].
source_table_name	STRING	Physical source table name (e.g., acc_t1) [1].
target_system	STRING	Target platform (e.g., SNOWFLAKE, DELTA_LAKE) [1].
target_table_name	STRING	Physical target table name (e.g., fac_t1) [1].
target_dataset_layer	STRING	Target layer (e.g., BRONZE, SILVER, FACILITY) [1].
opco	STRING	Ground/frieght/international
ingestion_mode	STRING	FULL, INCR, or CDC [1].
watermark_column	STRING	Column name to track delta (e.g., last_modified_ts) [1].
partition_col	STRING	Column name used to partition target data (e.g., load_date).
is_active	BOOL	Toggle to enable/disable pipeline runs [1].
data_quality_rules	JSON / TEXT	Validation rules config in JSON format [1].
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record insertion timestamp [1].
		
======================================

cdl_table_run_log		
		
Column Name	Data Type	Description
run_id	STRING	SHA-256 Hash of dag_id + execution_date.
dataset_id	STRING	Logical identifier for the pipeline mapping.
dag_run_date	DATE	Logical processing date (Airflow execution date as DATE).
dag_id	STRING	Airflow DAG Identifier.
task_id	STRING	Airflow Task Identifier.
dataset_layer	STRING	E.g., ACCOUNT (Source), FACILITY (Target).
opco	STRING	Ground/frieght/international
table_name	STRING	Name of the table being processed.
status	STRING	RUNNING, SUCCESS, FAILED, SKIPPED, HALTED.
attempt_number	INT64	Task retry attempt sequence (starts at 1).
rows_read	INT64	Records scanned from the source.
rows_written	INT64	Total records committed to the destination.
rows_rejected	INT64	Records failing inline DQ rules.
rows_merged	INT64	Merged records (for Upsert logic).
rows_inserted	INT64	Newly inserted records.
rows_updated	INT64	Updated records.
rows_deleted	INT64	Deleted records.
watermark_start	TIMESTAMP	Starting watermark (low-watermark).
watermark_end	TIMESTAMP	Ending watermark (high-watermark).
started_at	TIMESTAMP	System clock time when execution began.
completed_at	TIMESTAMP	System clock time when execution finished.
dq_results	JSON / TEXT	Structured JSON payload of DQ checks run.
error_code	STRING	Standardized error categorization code.
error_message	TEXT / STRING	Full stack trace / exception details.
updated_at	TIMESTAMP	System time when this row was last altered.
created_at	TIMESTAMP	Record creation timestamp (defaults to current time).
